[Course_Description]
Grow your Adobe XD skills with these pointers from Howard Pinsky, senior XD evangelist at Adobe. Howard goes over useful features and timesaving techniques that can help you make the most of this powerful design and prototyping tool. Each video provides suggestions for working more efficiently and effectively in XD, including how to best create hover interactions, animated UI elements, galleries of 3D cards for AR experiences, and more. Tune in each week for a new tip. Note: Because this is an ongoing series, viewers will not receive a certificate of completion.